{"id": "1210a065004a6c3661e44a381a7199372f80137cb11ebb59bf908df0cd7ab42d", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:0", "text": "Whilst Stylized Looks is far more than a simple toon shading system, it sure does render a beautiful toon if you so desire!"}
{"id": "a3403cf1fbd9381744041d320a64af0503acc380312b5384eb22033cadcae1ec", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:1", "text": "PxrStylizedToon"}
{"id": "dba9b4fe54973163f88562290942d11765a69a7b5ce721b43e5a07817b54a8b1", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:2", "text": "Visualizer"}
{"id": "f08d35913dbf8b31e7d4cbfa57100ed23bf7a3d1c8cbbff1d2b5354a9aadbf18", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:3", "text": "Use these settings to preview certain AOVs to aid in the development of your creative toonning!"}
{"id": "7d249ed4eb75246b3d0eee0799069b044136ea2d1fe30996b9f11fe59d8c1b2a", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:4", "text": "Beauty"}
{"id": "6d7d56712c2bad4e763438da0ed829cf38012f1ee2e86cc27bc533ecc853d68f", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:5", "text": "The Beauty AOV being rendered before the Stylized Looks filters are applied"}
{"id": "c7d5be701779f987f1892ca587223fda0efdbd5f5fd8bae4add4ee76756f9091", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:6", "text": "Toon Ramp"}
{"id": "56ea1ff2c8681c5997b4e1aef0496464c871442b1ce1a8f882dfc1cc3ed947e7", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:7", "text": "The Toon ramping."}
{"id": "8c945e790c00e0edb82072891f57e4f4f436a6bacff05c36575b7d5837f9e2f9", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:8", "text": "Toon Final"}
{"id": "07d0166f99b3e94a55f098e8eaf787d1fedaf76e7674fa26e9b518f6a3fa298e", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:9", "text": "Your beautiful toon image"}
{"id": "0ee996a6761de1be5f3ab77d2ada2c795b3585206b7c4a65432a2f09c5e6b0c2", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:10", "text": "Toon Final with Spec"}
{"id": "6c84d86a197de40e23ba6c801a8d4c57ef405328a4b5f84d12a2abb420f65481", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:11", "text": "Your beautiful toon image + specular highlights"}
{"id": "cd443b434b5b150bac81703bf30a52ad817d2fdfd76283428875aa707f01a657", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:12", "text": "Diffuse Energy"}
{"id": "f90d20808223ba9c6f3ea98fa338c6fed76f25456edc5fbcd4caaa09ee82e4bd", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:13", "text": "The energy emitted by the Diffuse AOV"}
{"id": "81d9065ae25b0fdae9d40ef24e1947f3028d376be77807b78daf2644a21254db", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:14", "text": "Diffuse Luminance"}
{"id": "a8b3248bbc9aa129f43498f459b60fbf27eed890ceb714b297020f054089f654", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:15", "text": "The luminance of the diffuse AOV"}
{"id": "74ba87de67adaefc9507b330b2d752d7346ded0f4a397b121cbd3aa9aba916b7", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:16", "text": "Albedo"}
{"id": "253933bf33d43e8211023a690e910b8361f159e44e9bd0633073385ba3728f2d", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:17", "text": "The Albedo AOV"}
{"id": "19568e0c387d2c303964dc6d7186c0532547c44c49c946aceed473ed73a71864", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:18", "text": "Signal AOV String"}
{"id": "3dcc48ee548842ec79331d3d987ef5c22a52ec54f4f66722aad58a71077218f3", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:19", "text": "Name of a color AOV to use for the signal to toon shading. Typically diffuse, but you can put any light AOV here. This AOV has to be setup in Maya/Katana/Houdini or DisplayFilter will exit."}
{"id": "17eef2aba21b4c5cc8683f356d21841c6b74c06c989412f2f1d0175859f1b518", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:20", "text": "Diffuse Energy from"}
{"id": "15aa4477653b6bee6725ccc141ca9c1e3f4ef70c92a3f010b7dc394d7b0f0618", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:21", "text": "Under the hood a white shader approximation is created based off the Signal AOV to drive the Toon response. By default using average of RGB components of Signal AOV, but can also divide Signal AOV lighting results with a pure albedo from NPRalbedo AOV or albedo AOV. If NPRalbedo AOV chosen, must set Albedo Color in Stylized Controller Pattern node."}
{"id": "e70fa71763aedf94adf16bf8251ec931ddac557b66aea5be69ce740396566ac4", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:22", "text": "Light Mask Switch"}
{"id": "083d3296cbcac92dfa13c7df4a5b0f9be11fe724445afdd772285f9aa9d7f35d", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:23", "text": "Use light aov defined in signal_aov_string above as mask for previously daisy-chained Stylized shaders and/or physically based lighting."}
{"id": "aac12d2932fb5124c2c020f7726baf79bca2a6e313a577b364115b7a11177d09", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:24", "text": "BG Color"}
{"id": "f1fcb6de4192309721a8c752bf92d405e31143fd9337e41bfd8e3ad71d41b512", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:25", "text": "Color of Background"}
{"id": "8d5d3eb86bbd46d873495135ba80695cec368ce6e89b6fe79a6dc614308196f7", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:26", "text": "Occl Integrator Switch"}
{"id": "28abd0b3c7c776b3f08cc0e3b71e00c44a4d12d69161b3ee92572700408b80b5", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:27", "text": "If Using Occlusion Integrator, turn this on"}
{"id": "8ae269313d8a416948854dda14c6b63a6bf0c5a3b95fb5ee686174f84c000c0f", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:28", "text": "Float Spline"}
{"id": "48262103ce39fe9c4f29c89ab0fac82eb4b72e77244c3fa23772c8372accaf4e", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:29", "text": "Remap Spline Switch"}
{"id": "65942f5d90802afd3c603f7933e66dace2c56c1d8db054f75c5577f931a0936e", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:31", "text": "Step Mode"}
{"id": "c19f99286525e70113ecdf4608982c3ae015bc50353598b8f3ab3959936fd65a", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:32", "text": "Albedo: steps to object albedo from albedo AOV. Light To Albedo: steps from white or light color to albedo color of object (use albedoLift to see more if dark albedo or textures). Darks Color: step to chosen color instead of default black."}
{"id": "d4dd0d7f7df9ce0f4b68b02c71612b3107057bbdf7964dfe2cfbe876bcb21691", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:33", "text": "Toon Diffuse Steps"}
{"id": "4c42281e20ac8d6de7a4988524a60fe8eb1fa5236433e03ebdb572a269d86272", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:34", "text": "Number of steps to quantize diffuse lighting"}
{"id": "a59cc47ec5820059dd190d07a64b6b55c72bbb90a0f4a8e58e888a799fe4ed85", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:35", "text": "Albedo Lift"}
{"id": "6d4b61d71e86ae203956010d7bd6a9e8486a5d70959eb463c0396fc31d709aad", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:36", "text": "When Step Mode = Albedo or Light to Albedo, you can use this to lift your albedo values"}
{"id": "9434f81a1ad85e4dc2034a574b3ed4b3cd629c56cedf83eca97b009a8957ebda", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:37", "text": "Darks"}
{"id": "f8108972254ad8a703b90bab759e9b5d4f91b382a3c3a15d8d653cb719a35f87", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:38", "text": "Color to step to"}
{"id": "89a72f037e39611ecd756ed5eaa62fde9447462af8470ff9a81a9f5e3de0c832", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:39", "text": "Linstep Min"}
{"id": "59de6c89316d33dd97d774d0c4cc1901b3eb607bbe2a33fc74887b89bed62beb", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:40", "text": "Min for min-max remap of stepping. Check the NPRtoonDiffRamp AOV to visualize."}
{"id": "35219ca2dbd1f8036a1da3e20da01353597c6e3957359476f67554ec9ecfee75", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:41", "text": "Linstep Max"}
{"id": "2baf61fe0b8b63c745dd8080c30193478018993a6047a3c9a8328f35a0d271d1", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:42", "text": "Max for min-max remap of stepping. Check the NPRtoonDiffRamp AOV to visualize."}
{"id": "52927d31ff105bdf31d3e2c51acf54bf6be260c1119a6ba99191d189ba3e072a", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:44", "text": "Gamma for toon diffuse ramp. Check the NPRtoonDiffRamp AOV to visualize."}
{"id": "ffc9ea4e87d94c60369aeabf8580c62a3e0575c299c3d80279a4ffcce8b649c7", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:45", "text": "Step to Albedo"}
{"id": "80fbeae0262fe1609d51cd48016952132a4e3e27bdbad568eb175effebaea84a", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:46", "text": "Step to Albedo Color of objects instead of Blacks. Still uses Blacks, but as a multiplier on the Albedo Color, so switch Blacks to a grayscale value."}
{"id": "5012b6f299c3d42be74700d1d5dc4de8d8af46914c7324b16fb13590c557f99d", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:47", "text": "Clean Toon with 1 Distant Light"}
{"id": "4bc469a2df6c3f76bc00b64e7307f6cc04e8bbc27db8e12890c902a22c026e11", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:48", "text": "Toon Tips"}
{"id": "21a5dfeadb69177597dcfcebc42941c7865395d56f8199b77eb95d867f62b690", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:49", "text": "Changing the integrator to PxrDirectLighting will result in a sharper toon image"}
{"id": "0304c24c900cb066edbfe04ca2e37edd47a36baff779ac110386394f1194ded8", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:50", "text": "To achieve a traditional sharper toon render, try using lights such as the PxrDistanceLight and PxrSphereLight"}
{"id": "e590ca3ef9a4d855cbd88bf4bd792b25754dc203d0469f308603b8834ba4cc3e", "item_id": "b33e6a95e5:51", "text": "To reduce noise in the Toon banding, use a PxrDistantLight, turn off bounces (either PxrDirectLighting integrator or 0 for Max Indirect Bounces in PxrPathTracer integrator)"}
